{
  "id": "adv_card_szk_51_01",
  "title": "兵藤雫",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_lesson-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_3d_lesson-01-000-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-02.m4a",
      "startTime": 3.3666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_51_01-szk001.m4a",
      "text": "今日もkanaさんのSNSは、素敵……\n……ハッ！　新しい、投稿……！",
      "startTime": 4.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_51_01-szk002.m4a",
      "text": "『今日もレッスン！　ライブに向けて頑張るよ～』……\nレッスン室を使うということは、事務所に来る……？",
      "startTime": 13,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-in-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 9300,
          "startTime": 22.3
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_51_01-szk003.m4a",
      "text": "これは、推しを拝めるチャンス……！\nドルオタダッシュで向かわなきゃ……！",
      "startTime": 20.4666662852,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_3d_office-01-000-noon",
      "startTime": 24.401881345
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_51_01-kan001.m4a",
      "text": "ねぇ、さくら\n昨日やってたドラマなんだけどさー",
      "startTime": 27.0333335876,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 3099.998982799999,
          "startTime": 30.1333325704
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_51_01-szk004.m4a",
      "text": "（いた……！　生のkanaさん、今日も可愛い……！）\n（何度見ても眼福、ありがたや……）",
      "startTime": 36.4666665395,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_51_01-kan002.m4a",
      "text": "……あれ？　あそこにいるのってサニピの子じゃん",
      "startTime": 40.0730376561,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_51_01-szk005.m4a",
      "text": "（わっ！　こっち見た……！　目線は嬉しいけど）\n（ど、どどど、ど、どうしよう……）",
      "startTime": 48.7666637421,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_51_01-skr001.m4a",
      "text": "雫ちゃ～ん、昨日のドラマ観た？\n今、kanaさんと話してたんだけど",
      "startTime": 55.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_51_01-szk006.m4a",
      "text": "う、う、あ……\nド、ドラ、マママ、マ……！？",
      "startTime": 60.9340788524,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_51_01-kan003.m4a",
      "text": "……？　何？　お腹でも痛いの？",
      "startTime": 64.1831942241,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_51_01-szk007.m4a",
      "text": "（か、kanaさんに話し掛けられちゃった！）\n（まともに話したことないのに、なんて言えば……！？）",
      "startTime": 71.7007465363,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_51_01-szk008.m4a",
      "text": "（と、とと、と、とりあえず、お腹は痛くないって）\n（言わなきゃ！　あと、ドラマの話、だよね……！）",
      "startTime": 79.2007465363,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_51_01-szk009.m4a",
      "text": "お、お……\nお腹が面白かった！　ですっ！！",
      "startTime": 84.667413203,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 8799.998855500007,
          "startTime": 93.4674120585
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_51_01-kan004.m4a",
      "text": "……は？\nあ、ヤバ。そろそろ練習あるから行くわ",
      "startTime": 89.7674101512,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_51_01-skr002.m4a",
      "text": "雫ちゃん、どうしたの？\nなんだか様子が変だよ",
      "startTime": 97.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_51_01-szk010.m4a",
      "text": "うぅ……じ、実は……",
      "startTime": 100.6181265673,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_51_01-skr003.m4a",
      "text": "へ～、雫ちゃん、kanaさんのファンだったんだね！\nそれで緊張してたんだ～",
      "startTime": 112.9333323161,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_51_01-szk011.m4a",
      "text": "うん。スリクスのメンバーは、みんな憧れ\nでも、好き過ぎて、緊張しちゃって……",
      "startTime": 120.9947512945,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_51_01-szk012.m4a",
      "text": "本当は、サインしてもらったり、一緒にツーショットを\n撮ったりしてみたいんだけど……機会もなくて……",
      "startTime": 129.7517222884,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_51_01-skr004.m4a",
      "text": "うーん、機会かぁ……。あ、そういえば雫ちゃん\n雑誌のお誕生日企画の話が来てなかったっけ",
      "startTime": 142.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_51_01-szk013.m4a",
      "text": "『ミラクル☆アイドルバースデー！』のこと？\n編集部の人が、お願い事を叶えてくれる、夢の企画……",
      "startTime": 149.2147516569,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_51_01-skr005.m4a",
      "text": "その企画で、お願いしてみたらどうかな？\nkanaさんのサインとツーショット写真がほしいって",
      "startTime": 158.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_51_01-szk014.m4a",
      "text": "な、なんて大胆なお願い……！　でも、いい機会\nなのかも。kanaさん、参加してくれるかな？",
      "startTime": 167.3067245484,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_51_01-skr006.m4a",
      "text": "一応お仕事っていう扱いだし\nkanaさん優しいから、引き受けてくれるよ！",
      "startTime": 175.3333282471,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 179.9776751599
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 179.9776751599
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 180.2276751599
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_51_01-kan005.m4a",
      "text": "いーやーだ",
      "startTime": 181.0276751599,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 183.8850674829
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_51_01-szk015.m4a",
      "text": "がーん……\nグッバイ……私の、お誕生日……",
      "startTime": 186.561073653,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_51_01-skr007.m4a",
      "text": "し、雫ちゃん、落ち込むのは早いよ！\nまだ一度お願いしただけだから",
      "startTime": 193.9666615804,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 196.7387408298
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_51_01-kan006.m4a",
      "text": "何度頼んでもダメだっての。そもそもサインして\n写真撮るだけの企画、盛り上がる訳ないじゃん",
      "startTime": 201.4206659,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 205.2678336503
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_51_01-kan007.m4a",
      "text": "せめてさー、もっとお願い事を増やして尺稼ぐとか\n工夫の仕方思いつかない訳？",
      "startTime": 210.0539992333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 212.7611670217
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_51_01-szk016.m4a",
      "text": "え……\nそんなに沢山お願いして、いいんですか……？",
      "startTime": 213.8873325666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 217.6760648133
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_51_01-kan008.m4a",
      "text": "いや、例えばって話な",
      "startTime": 217.6760648133,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 220.0760648133
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_51_01-skr008.m4a",
      "text": "つまり！　い～～～～っぱいお願いを増やせば\n参加してくれるっていうことですねっ！？",
      "startTime": 225.0333282471,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 228.0304640176
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
